        String str1="abcdef";//ab6cdef,abBcdef
        System.out.println(str1.matches("[abc]*"));*/ -> any number of times but should contain only abc
        
        
        /*String str1="accbdefg";//accb
        System.out.println(str1.matches("[abc]{3,7}"));*/-> should contain abc any number of times but minimum length should be 3 and max is 7
        
        String str1="john@gmail.com";
        //System.out.println(str1.matches(".*gmail.*")); -> can contain any letters and any number of letters but it should have gmail
        System.out.println(str1.matches("\\w*@gmail(.*)")); -> can have alphabets or numbers any number of time but should have @gmail and after that
        can have any letters any number of times